dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Cajon quadrangle, San Bernardino County, California
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle CAJON, CA 1988, DMA 2552 IV SW-Series V895"
"Prepared in cooperation with the Angeles National Forest."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, index to sources of geology, and 1 col. cross section.
